Title: Crimson Valley
Description:
A fall-themed valley full of cliffs, caves and structures.
The AI may be a little wonky sometimes because of the large amount of obstacles.
Also be careful, enemies can hide on trees!

3 bronze, 3 silver, 3 gold, 3 diamond, 3 titanium, 3 uranium, 3 insanium.

If you enjoyed this arena, checkout [url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2248552820]Rune Valley[/url] as well!
